# Super Store Sales Dashboard

## Overview
An interactive Power BI dashboard built using the Super Store dataset to analyze sales, profit, quantity, and regional performance.

## Features
- Sales KPI
- Sales by Category
- Sales by Segment
- Sales by Payment Mode
- Sales by Ship Mode
- Monthly Sales Trend
- Monthly Quantity Trend
- Sales by State (Map)
- Regional Filters

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX
- Power Query

## Dataset
Super Store Sales Dataset

